PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of certain persons as part-time directors of the board of directors of the Saint John Port Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years. (MALCOLM R. BAXTER, Saint John, New Brunswick, in the place of William M. Thompson, whose term has expired; KERI LEA WALKER, Sussex, New Brunswick, effective May 18, 1995, in the place of Kenneth J. Bourque, whose term will expire; and WILLIAM R. LEAHY, Saint John, New Brunswick, in the place of Shirley A. McAlary, whose term has expired)
